# Job Applier Rules

Automates application submission via browser (Camoufox); form filling, screenshots, step traces.

## Scope
- Apply command intake
- Application execution coordinator
- Domain/applier strategy interfaces
- Step trace updates
- Screenshot artifact registration
- Result callbacks to control service

## Do NOT
- Own user management
- Own matching logic
- Own fetcher logic
- Bury domain-specific automation in generic control code

## Conventions
- Use browser primitives; domain strategies use them
- Report step traces cleanly
- One strategy per domain/board
